<br>
I came to Iceclad, I saw a little halfling druid from Kaze by the gnolls, he said, look, Lodizal's up.  I said &quot;WOOT&quot; very excited because I had been camping him for a few days, in hopes of getting the map for my Eyepatch of Plunder (map was last piece I needed) I tell all my friends.  My level 60 cleric friend comes (ehrnam) and we start talking.  He gets a 60 rogue, 2 58 wizzies, 56 bard, and some more there, while I bring in my friends from Vision which included a 57 warrior, 60 cleric, 59 shaman, 59 bard, etc.  By this time, Ehrnam and I were kiting Lodizal for about 10 minutes, waiting for our friends.  When they all arrived, we notice Ikonos (druid, who is still cool =P) pop up.  I said hey, Lodizal's up for me! and he said, something along the lines of not for long. (dont remember exact words, but they were similar) now then, I see some Landslide people file into the zone, there were 16.  While Ehrnam kited Lodizal, he turned around and noticed it was gone.  He traced back and saw Kiliky (bard) running with Lodizal on her back to the Landslide camp.  When my friends got to their camp, the last fireball struck Lodizal and he fell.  I was angry at this point, but I was still in hope of getting the map, since we did have it first.  I talk to their leader, and he said Kiliky had it first (which is not possible, because none of them were in the zone at the time when we were kiting) so then I start talking to Ikonos.  He dropped the map, shell, boots, ring, and 4 spells. First item to lotto (only no drop item there) was the map.  I see some people roll, I roll 69 969 like the rest of them, and come up with 870 something.  I also offered to pay 3000p to loot the map.  Now I wait a few minutes, and still have the highest roll, Kiliky then rolls, and gets a 940 something.  She goes and loots the map.  Well, at this time, I was fumed.  I was shouting at my friends and things, and they were all tict off also. We went back, and now I have to camp Lodizal again.  so in conclusion, those 16 members of Landslide have lost all my respect.  They had no right whatsoever to pull off Lodizal from Ehrnam, then when they find out, to kill him, and not let the 1 item the person wanted to be looted.  Now i HATE posting stuff like this, and this is only my 2nd time, but I am back camping Lodizal, and hopefully will not be Kill Stealed next time, so thanks for reading, and Landslide, be more careful what you do, and how you act, it affects all your reputation.<br>
<br>
